Day 1: Grandma's Magic Basket

Grandma Meera has a magical basket filled with golden apples. Every apple has a special number engraved on it. Today, she gives you one of these apples and tells you:
“The number on this apple hides a secret. If you can find the sum of its digits, I’ll tell you the next clue in our treasure hunt!”
Curious and excited, you look at the number on the apple. Can you help Grandma Meera by uncovering the secret?

Your Task: Given a number engraved on the apple, calculate the sum of its digits
Input: A single integer n, (0 ≤ n ≤ 10^9)
Output: Print Sum of digits of n

Give it a try.... Follow for more
Solution: Grandmas_Magic_Basket.py



